{"tid":2282254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［有圖］立場：理大外現「光復香港」、「SAVE 12」鎖頭掛鐵網拼字","createTime":"2020-11-11T17:20:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T05:23:17.000Z","uid":22556,"like":526,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"e100fabe8aa10b9d2446b3bf16ca0edb852bd22d","tid":2282254,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T17:20:06.000Z","msg":"【理大外現「光復香港」、「SAVE 12」鎖頭掛鐵網拼字】<br />\n<br />\n「理大圍城」發生將近一年，《立場》接獲讀者提供相片，理工大學外接駁紅磡火車站的天橋，今（12 日）凌晨出現「光復香港」及「SAVE 12」字句。<br />\n<br />\n理大事件後，接駁校園的天橋上加裝了鐵網，至今仍然存在；從相片所見，字句由無數個彩色鎖頭拼湊而成。<br />\n<br />\n（讀者提供相片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uyAyJA8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuyAyJA8.jpg&h=3ee34090&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3635976876487906/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F3635976876487906%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Auybpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=edd707c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3635976876487906/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"07acaa790df520cf42869bff8abb0465bece612d","tid":2282254,"uid":199479,"like":16,"dislike":61,"score":-45,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T17:24:51.000Z","msg":"成個鐵網拆左佢就搞掂"},{"pid":"3f5dd115210bb3f607fbc0939ed2cdf715796469","tid":2282254,"uid":241331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T17:25:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a20c63571813f3aeb339a816cd3109ad47f7ae2e","tid":2282254,"uid":137037,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T17:26:21.000Z","msg":"好有心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d59ce2e80c9f2d87f2c63cdf0a4c8781ac6f7ebd","tid":2282254,"uid":61020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T17:27:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62375dd94dd